  "title": "Assistant Engineer/ Technician x10 (Marine/ Aviation/ Engineering) – 5 Day [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefit:</strong></p><ul><li><p>5 days Work</p></li><li><p>Entry Level are welcome!</p></li><li><p>Various industries: Aviation/ Marine/ Automotive/ Enginering Solutions</p></li><li><p>Multiple locations hiring: West/ North/ East</p></li><li><p>Basic Salary : $2200 - $3200 </p></li><li><p>Good Allowance, Bonus and AWS</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform on-site servicing, maintenance, and troubleshooting of various machinery and systems to ensure seamless operations.</p></li><li><p>Monitor and maintain equipment performance, ensuring all systems run efficiently and reliably.</p></li><li><p>Support the installation, setup, and commissioning of new machines and equipment.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with engineers and technicians to facilitate smooth daily operations and technical support.</p></li><li><p>Respond promptly to client service calls, diagnosing and resolving technical issues efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Conduct routine inspections to ensure equipment remains in top condition and meets performance standards.</p></li><li><p>Plan and carry out preventive maintenance schedules to reduce downtime and extend the lifespan of machinery.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min Nitec/ Higher Nitec/ Diploma in Electrical/ Mechanical/ Marine or other engineering related</p></li><li><p>2 years relevant experiences will be advantage</p></li><li><p>Entry level welcome to apply, training will be provided</p></li></ul><p><br />To Apply, kindly click on the \"<strong>APPLY NOW</strong>\" button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</p>",
